Godzillawars Source Alpha 1 Pseudo Story: Evil Terrorists foundet their Evil Terrorist Camp on a little Island. But then the American Government tested Nuclear Weapons on the Island. Some of the Terrorists not died in these Tests, and now theyre Mutated into Giant Terrorists and want to rule the World. The Only Chance for the Government is to make a force of Nuclear Counter-Terrorists to beat them. Now the Terrorists are on their way to a city, but this time they get unexpected Guests. This is my first map, created using Hammer. I chose a gungame style map, because it's my favorite game-style and the simplicity made it easy to adapt.

The map is based on a gg_deagle5 style obstacle labyrinth, but with added functionality on the sides.

All credit to the creator of the deagle5 style for my inspiration.

Please rate and comment with tips and PLEASE tell me if I screwed anything up..remember, this is my FIRST attempt at map making, and I only want to get better.

**INSTALLATION**
Extract files to steamapps\YOURNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
or extract to any location and copy then paste into your maps folder.

That simple!

COMMENTS: No third-party/third-person testing was done before the release of this map. If you have any problems, tell me on my FPSBanana page ("WEBSITE"), the EF forums (URL above), or e-mail me. Copyright 2007 Grae Matter Studios some rights reserved.

It incorporates many elements of popular gg maps including multi-levels, water, ladders, stairs, bright lighting, a custom skybox, a "dust" texture theme, sniper zones, maze zones, indoor and outdoor strategic points, asymmetrical but balanced spawns, and a dimension which lends itself to quick rounds.

Wanted a desert setting for a deagle variant. The 'crates' are in the general shape and placement of the original but I made the entire middle area has been expanded, (along with the outer walk ways), and different structures have been added. While this is definitely not a re-texture of deagle I wanted the overall feel of the tight quarters. The entire top section of the perimeter is off limits to the player. In a couple of places, you can get up to that invisible barrier, but you can't cross it. 
As with all my maps, if you happen to have feedback, please leave a comment. Also, I'm willing to make anyone custom versions of my maps with your logos or whatever inside, just let me know!
Here's a link to a video of the map if you want a better look at it before downloading.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n8yeT6H8YK0

Ge_tower version 6

By os-Genome

Terrorists have taken over a very weird looking tower which has a spinny light thing at the top.

Objective is to kill all enemies. There are three ways for the CTs to reach the top of the tower. A ladder on the outside of the tower, an elevator, and a ladder behind the elevator. Beware of explosive barrels.

CT:  Kill the terrorists.

T:  Kill the counter-terrorists.

HINT: You can shoot the barrels before they fall down, killing the people who released them.

And don't block the elevator. You'll die in exactly 0.6 seconds.
